songs.title: Interlude
songs.lyrics:
[Interlude: Cedric The Entertainer]
Goin' good, hold up. Get off me real quick, I'm tryin' to holla at my dawg real fast
Hey, hey, Nelly what's up, dog?
This Ced the Entertainer, boy
I'm at a wild little party, dog
Hey get back at me, I'm tryin' to holla at you about the album now
I'ma talk to all of ya'll
Big League, Kyuan, Little T, City Spud, my homies
What's up, ya'll, you need to get at me, I need to be on this album player
I'm tryin' to blow up with ya. S.T.L
Y'all get back at me, aight? Just call me
